<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.199714>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Parartemia laticaudata sp. nov. A, male head with antennae; B, dorsal view of male thorax and abdomen, C, male gonopods; D, expanded penis; E, female head; F, dorsal view of female thorax and abdomen T 8 to A 4. Scale bars 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/199714/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

